  </zone>
  <zone type="main">
    <line rend="indent1">Which wraps me, like an atmosphere of light</line>
    <line>And bears me as a cloud is borne by its own wind<add place="sublinear">!</add></line>
    <milestone unit="tei:speaker" spanTo="#e1-0023.01"/>
    <line rend="center">The Moon</line>
    <anchor xml:id="e1-0023.01"/>
    <line rend="indent1">Brother mine, calm wanderer</line>
    <line rend="indent1">Happy globe of land &amp; air</line>
    <line>Some Spirit <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">wraps th<mod>
            <del rend="overwritten">y</del>
            <add place="intralinear">ine</add>
          </mod> atmosphere &amp;</del>
        <add place="superlinear">is darted like a beam from</add>
      </mod> thee</line>
    <line rend="indent1">Which penetrates my frozen frame</line>
    <line rend="indent1">And passes with the warmth of flame&#x2014;</line>
    <line>With love &amp; odour &amp; deep melody</line>
    <line rend="indent2"><retrace cause="unclear">T</retrace>hrough me, through me!&#x2014;</line>
    <milestone unit="tei:speaker" spanTo="#e1-0023.02"/>
    <line rend="center">The Earth</line>
    <anchor xml:id="e1-0023.02"/>
    <line>Ha, ha,! the cavens of my hollow mountains</line>
    <line>My cloven fire-crags, sound-exulting fountains</line>
    <line>Laugh with a vast &amp; inextinguishable laughter</line>
    <line rend="indent1">The Oceans &amp; the Desarts &amp; the Abysses</line>
    <line rend="indent1">Of the deep air's un<mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">fathomed</del>
        <add place="superlinear">measured</add>
      </mod> wildernesses</line>
    <line>Answer from <mod>
        <add place="sublinear"><metamark function="insert">^</metamark></add>
        <add place="superlinear">all</add>
      </mod> their clouds &amp; billows, echoing after</line>
    <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" extent="1" />
    <line rend="indent1">They cry aloud as I do&#x2014; Sceptered Curse</line>
    <line rend="indent1">Who all our green &amp; azure Universe</line>
  </zone>
